 <span data-ttu-id="4a0c7-328">の`minRepeat`値は、0以上、の`maxRepeat`値以下である必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4a0c7-328">The value of `minRepeat` must be greater than or equal to 0 and less than or equal to the value of `maxRepeat`.</span></span>  
  
